{"tid":1308634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔好再屌連儂牆] 只貼不守咪解決左個問題","createTime":"2019-07-12T02:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T16:25:58.000Z","uid":104803,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"13eb77efe47a9d2d606f88b1562519ede2e7637c","tid":1308634,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:48:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">大佬見到有人寫字，<br />\n就見字如見人知道有人同行<br />\n好L大鼓勵<br />\n<br />\n覺得分散左人既話，咁咪只貼不守、遍地開花囉<br />\n點解講到連儂牆好大問題，搞到要放棄用呢樣野鼓勵大家？？？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">貼張memo紙兩三秒姐<br />\n講到貼左張memo個運動就失敗咁到底做乜9？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">一出門口去集合點途中邊行邊貼，咪又鼓勵到人又抗爭到。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">call機時大家響應到就得啦。<br />\n<br />\n轉個方式後，遍地開花仲可以比公眾見到我地無比人一打就放棄，而係be water，不斷進步不斷改變，持續抗爭</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGCOzLB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGCOzLB.png&h=84539549&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"453bc9257bec388634513d8fa2ac441b97e81298","tid":1308634,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:48:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"325e701907e8af774d57f209a6cfe8e335de3656","tid":1308634,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:49:09.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"f5659fb0e1dd17aa764c1613ce62ae8cfe7d203c","tid":1308634,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:49:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62558dba28da00e5df46b5a6de04dcf790f20033","tid":1308634,"uid":32221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:51:50.000Z","msg":"其實有人得閒想望住未由得佢<br />\n以勸既係阻止<br />\n有人搞未企遠啲影下大頭表揚下算"},{"pid":"cdf16615979e5e958b343a638e1f34333dc91478","tid":1308634,"uid":276150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:53:39.000Z","msg":"贊成呀，冇咗咪再貼囉，唔好浪費太多精力去守或者去糾纏。行過又貼下，永不止息咁，唔使守。"},{"pid":"bf4d52fa5ca852ab4d460a2b19811749ead298f3","tid":1308634,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:54:05.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"9774edd19873d1789cfbe731c7263ee716b57ffd","tid":1308634,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:54:45.000Z","msg":"[五毛分化警示] 散佈失敗論，叫人聚焦，放棄其他野，去金鐘，乃一貫分化技倆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e16a1bf2dd4ccbcd969f2aea68556875b5074f54","tid":1308634,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1b89fbf964928d24b6c68c9948391b728e30147","tid":1308634,"uid":252684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"完全同意"},{"pid":"8bbb8ee4be837d97bd0e1832c3ab29c0a281470b","tid":1308634,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:58:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c111b72101ec18bf9a30e62bc55c421a2293925f","tid":1308634,"uid":32221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"想留守隨便<br />\n有個別人要撕就行遠影相<b